metadata.name: Headliners #1 - Man Bites Dog
metadata.description: The Headliners Collection is AI generated NFTs as commentary to traditional news media headlines. "Man Bites Dog" is a classic aphorism use to articulate the difference between what is, and is not, newsworthy. We've updated this story by placing both parties on Mars during their tussle.

attributes.value: Japanese Superflat: Man in spacesuit bites dog on Mars
